    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >想找一款轻松愉快又不阴郁的 Metroidvania？我们已经为您准备好了。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>露珠王朝》（Dewdrop Dynasty）</strong></i><strong>是一款快节奏、枪战跳跃的 Metroidvania 游戏，具有独特的复古像素艺术风格。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1444080/extras/c19ab3b8edcf1d9b0883655791c6a844.apng?t=1770669512\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1444080/extras/c19ab3b8edcf1d9b0883655791c6a844.poster.avif?t=1770669512\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=87 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在露珠世界中射击、跳跃和探索--这片相互连接的土地上充满了隐藏的秘密、多样的生物群落、奇怪的怪物和更奇怪的居民。   </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >  </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >露珠王朝》中有太多需要探索的地方、需要面对的老板和需要解决的谜题，它充满了魅力、挑战和快节奏的乐趣。<strong>露珠王朝》的世界不会自己探索，您还在等什么呢？</strong> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1444080/extras/06d3c72422163810bc204a1c3b833133.apng?t=1770669512\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1444080/extras/06d3c72422163810bc204a1c3b833133.poster.avif?t=1770669512\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=102 /></picture></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1444080/extras/960a2d906241cfe74076ac7ca5a96bba.webp?t=1770669512\" width=20 height=14 /></span> 跳枪、擦枪动作，激发你内心的神枪手精神</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1444080/extras/8bc7b2e4b116235762dd0ca3805253c2.webp?t=1770669512\" width=20 height=20 /></span> 从自动售货机上收集和兑换奖券，以获得有趣的奖品</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1444080/extras/3deabea7a018325c1b4ba4f17a9d651e.webp?t=1770669512\" width=24 height=20 /></span> 解锁和挥舞独特的物品和奇特的能力</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1444080/extras/6ac436185874158274c27a781fb5c14c.webp?t=1770669512\" width=24 height=14 /></span> 戴各种愚蠢、时尚、偶尔有用的帽子</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1444080/extras/aee6441e21e22313ef07ce607d124b32.webp?t=1770669512\" width=22 height=26 /></span> 享受充满个性的多彩像素艺术风格</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1444080/extras/62ff290a56db130be8d3b63ed8652dfb.webp?t=1770669512\" width=20 height=20 /></span> 在探索露珠世界的过程中标注地图</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1444080/extras/5ba5862d309a11630eab679c3fc4b35c.webp?t=1770669512\" width=26 height=20 /></span> 使用沿途收集的物品，与 Boss 和古怪的敌人展开对决</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1444080/extras/a11da29f135b5c73696c07baca985c72.webp?t=1770669512\" width=24 height=26 /></span> 探索一个充满魅力、幽默和古怪角色的轻松世界</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1444080/extras/9e9bb4dbdb7f848d889d88cb017adb73.webp?t=1770669512\" width=20 height=20 /></span> 此外，还有才华<strong>横溢的彼得-里德-琼斯创</strong>作的原声音乐</p>",
